00:33:01.910 --> 00:33:02.910
La persona detrás de esto

00:33:03.310 --> 00:33:04.231
debe ser formidable.

00:33:04.231 --> 00:33:07.014
(Casa de Lianwei)

00:33:08.584 --> 00:33:10.720
